Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.70,0:01:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇 萬里晴空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.64,0:01:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 今天也要拜託妳看家囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.94,0:01:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.34,0:01:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家好 我是本田透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.88,0:01:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那年五月獨自撫養我的媽媽因為車禍而過世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.49,0:01:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我現在住在祕密的帳篷裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.23,0:01:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然談不上很快樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.33,0:01:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.70,0:01:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的優點是不管什麼時候都不會退縮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.50,0:02:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.57,0:02:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 大發現 這裡蓋了一棟房子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.64,0:02:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我停下來看一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.15,0:02:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.11,0:02:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛 是十二生肖的擺飾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.15,0:02:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.92,0:02:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡怎麼會有女孩子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.49,0:02:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊、不、不好意思 我擅自看了一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.40,0:02:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 我拿出來曬的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.30,0:02:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 年輕人看了應該會覺得沒什麼意思吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.87,0:02:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不、不會很可愛呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.74,0:02:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 我很高興呢 我也很喜歡哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.08,0:02:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 終究還是沒有貓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.55,0:02:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貓？哦 妳是指十二生肖中有關貓的事情啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.82,0:02:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 媽媽經常對我提起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.70,0:03:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很久很久以前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.30,0:03:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神對動物們說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.27,0:03:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天我要開一個宴會招待你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.97,0:03:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不能遲到啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.48,0:03:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了這一席話 喜歡惡作劇的老鼠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.91,0:03:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,騙住在附近的貓說宴會後天才要舉行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.19,0:03:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隔天 老鼠騎在牛背上來到宴會場輕巧的著地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.36,0:03:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨後來到的是牛、老虎 宴會熱鬧地一直開到早上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.90,0:03:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有受騙的貓毫不知情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.84,0:03:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透 妳為什麼哭呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.84,0:03:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為人家覺得貓咪他好可憐哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.44,0:03:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我決定了 我要把狗換掉 用貓來代替
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.21,0:03:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦 那傢伙要是聽到的話不曉得會有什麼表情呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.72,0:03:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.58,0:03:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是屬狗的吧 有一種親切感呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.95,0:04:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我也是屬狗的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.06,0:04:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一不注意你就跩起來了 妳還好吧？本田同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.23,0:04:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我表哥沒有做什麼失禮的事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.17,0:04:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,草 草摩同學！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.77,0:04:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 好像在作夢哦 是草摩同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.17,0:04:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們學校的王子草摩由希同學就在我的眼前呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.81,0:04:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這書包很重呢 裡面有裝字典嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.01,0:04:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來這裡是草摩由希的家呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.55,0:04:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 裝了兩本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.59,0:04:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘩 原來是由希的同學啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.69,0:04:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我重新自我介紹吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.33,0:04:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫草摩紫吳 是由希的表哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.30,0:04:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我是本田透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.16,0:04:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本田同學 妳怎麼會在這裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.50,0:04:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我家就在附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.70,0:04:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,附近這一帶？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.37,0:04:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是、是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.84,0:04:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.34,0:04:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那、那我先告辭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.81,0:04:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 本田同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.84,0:04:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.91,0:04:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難得碰到 我們一起走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.45,0:05:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.75,0:05:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L‧O‧V‧E LOVELY 由希！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.56,0:05:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本田同學！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.03,0:05:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這究竟是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.77,0:05:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼妳會和草摩一起上學 我希望妳能說明清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.40,0:05:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只、只是碰巧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.40,0:05:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是什麼事都用碰巧當藉口的話那就不需要警察了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.51,0:05:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果說起海原高校1年D班的草摩由希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.61,0:05:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對所有的女學生來說是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.94,0:05:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無人不知 無人不曉的俊俏瀟灑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.05,0:05:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聰明絕倫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.01,0:05:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,文武雙全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.08,0:05:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就連身為由希王子愛好會的我們都沒有機會接近他！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.29,0:05:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.69,0:05:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.12,0:05:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透說她只是碰巧遇上的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.76,0:05:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳們也別再胡鬧下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.83,0:05:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什 什麼嘛 太妹 別以為我們會善罷甘休
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.96,0:05:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們 看我用毒電波對付你們！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.84,0:05:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小魚、小花 多謝妳們救了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.11,0:06:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是場無妄之災啊～小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.44,0:06:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花島 妳可別真的送出電波哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.91,0:06:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,草摩同學真的太美形了 光在旁邊看就會令人緊張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.22,0:06:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連話都說不出來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.99,0:06:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我感覺到他散發出奇妙的電波
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.33,0:06:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又來了 花島的電波情報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.70,0:06:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇妙是指？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.90,0:06:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個我也不太清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.10,0:06:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確實很神祕 他好像不太喜歡談自己的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.90,0:06:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之前有一個二年級的女孩想對他告白而想抱他 結果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.18,0:06:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然用力把對方推開 連自己都嚇了一大跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.61,0:06:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在熱情的高中生真奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.18,0:06:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝、謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.05,0:06:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳今天也要去打工嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.55,0:06:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.42,0:06:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真辛苦 妳還是被爺爺撫養吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.60,0:06:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.10,0:06:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們說好學費由妳自己付吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.03,0:06:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是、是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.70,0:07:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.97,0:07:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,縣立高中的學費也沒多貴 應該不至於要妳去打工吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.98,0:07:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這、這是因為…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.61,0:07:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳的飯都是我供應的 所以妳打工賺的錢應該有剩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.45,0:07:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是、是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.72,0:07:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳應該早點說的嘛 這樣我就會跟妳收錢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.59,0:07:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.86,0:07:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能說 不能告訴小魚和小花我住在帳篷裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.06,0:07:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自從爸爸病故之後 為生活不停工作的媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.77,0:07:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總是那麼充滿活力 開朗的媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.78,0:07:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本不會想到她會因為車禍而過世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.51,0:07:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很多人都想要照顧我 不過最後決定到爺爺家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.62,0:07:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了不增加以退休金為生的爺爺的負擔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.89,0:08:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以當初說好學費由我自己付
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.40,0:08:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 由於姑姑夫妻要和爺爺一起住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.87,0:08:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以房子要改建 於是這段期間要我去朋友家住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.58,0:08:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小魚家裡只有一房一廳 小花家裡有五個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.15,0:08:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能為她們添麻煩 可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.79,0:08:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.39,0:08:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都是獨自一個人 這可是個天大的好機會！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.46,0:08:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 草摩同學 今天早上真謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.03,0:08:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才要道謝呢 紫吳害妳添麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.80,0:08:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 他很不錯啊 還讓我看十二生肖的飾品呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.28,0:08:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 妳還說希望自己屬貓 對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.52,0:08:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是個怪小孩嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.68,0:09:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貓最蠢了 習慣也不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.52,0:09:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.20,0:09:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳知道嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.80,0:09:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十二生肖本來是十干十二支
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.10,0:09:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.91,0:09:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原本是用來計數或是計時的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.84,0:09:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,後來加入了陰陽五行相生相剋來占卜吉凶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.25,0:09:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和動物沒有關係嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.05,0:09:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不知道什麼時候開始基於什麼理由加入了動物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.13,0:09:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 一開始十二生肖就沒有讓貓加入的空間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.70,0:09:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 就算是加入十二生肖也沒什麼了不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.61,0:09:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貓真是蠢斃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.51,0:10:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 這麼說來 草摩同學不喜歡貓囉？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.59,0:10:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我今天早上就覺得妳的臉色不太好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.06,0:10:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳還是多注意一下身體比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.76,0:10:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 明天見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.67,0:10:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的好神祕哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.90,0:10:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過草摩同學他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.41,0:10:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.67,0:10:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就當做沒聽見好了 媽媽以前更辛苦呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.08,0:10:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歐巴桑 快來收這裡的垃圾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.38,0:10:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.98,0:10:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能沮喪 NEVER GIVE UP！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.89,0:10:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉～每天吃外面 都吃膩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.23,0:10:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你來做飯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.50,0:10:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我做飯你又會抱怨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.60,0:10:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在咖哩飯裡面加醃蘿蔔 我想誰都會抱怨吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.84,0:10:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你那麼聰明 可是對家事卻一竅不通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.97,0:11:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看我們請個女傭好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.04,0:11:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女人很麻煩耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.58,0:11:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.42,0:11:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.32,0:11:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本田同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.95,0:11:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 我現在好睏哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.92,0:11:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是今天一定要把作業寫完才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.93,0:11:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用小溪的水洗把臉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.44,0:11:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紫吳 你笑太久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.69,0:11:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.49,0:11:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以妳住在帳篷裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.59,0:11:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.59,0:11:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候開始的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.86,0:11:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大約一個星期之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.26,0:11:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才覺得奇怪呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.29,0:11:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一帶是草摩家的土地 沒有說租人或是賣掉啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.00,0:11:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求求你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.97,0:12:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暫時讓我借用一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.24,0:12:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等房子改建好我馬上搬走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.01,0:12:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我沒什麼錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.64,0:12:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我願意付錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.67,0:12:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求求你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.84,0:12:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那裡很危險哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.18,0:12:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,山崖的土很鬆軟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.65,0:12:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還經常有色狼出沒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.05,0:12:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更何況一個女孩子要在帳篷裡生活好幾個月 不太可能吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.18,0:12:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你笑完啦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.32,0:12:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.02,0:12:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.15,0:12:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我連蝸牛都不怕 而且我對體力和精神都很有自信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.26,0:12:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本田同學！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.29,0:12:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在發燒呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.29,0:12:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快去找冰塊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.23,0:12:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.90,0:12:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,腐…腐海的森林
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.43,0:12:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是不錯的比喻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.64,0:12:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.44,0:12:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那片山崖馬上就要崩塌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.31,0:12:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…你怎麼知道？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.42,0:12:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概是野性的直覺吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.49,0:12:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.75,0:12:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在這附近吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.16,0:12:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概是帳篷附近吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.66,0:12:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.86,0:13:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟、糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.86,0:13:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帳篷裡有媽媽的照片！媽媽！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.14,0:13:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本田同學 冷靜點 妳在發燒呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.47,0:13:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 媽媽她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.94,0:13:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.11,0:13:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不快點拿出來的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.78,0:13:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽會很痛苦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.41,0:13:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等天亮之後再來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.25,0:13:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是再塌一次而害妳受傷的話 妳媽媽會更難過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.83,0:13:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由希去找冰塊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.57,0:13:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.67,0:13:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳很累了吧 妳可能硬撐太久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.17,0:13:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在連家都沒有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.05,0:13:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很難過嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.81,0:13:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 還遭遇過更痛苦的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.09,0:14:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.69,0:14:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽因車禍過世的那個早上 我沒有說路上小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.90,0:14:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為有小考
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.77,0:14:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直熬夜到早上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.34,0:14:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以起不來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.55,0:14:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有那天沒有說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.28,0:14:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平常都會說的 只有那個早上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.33,0:14:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想去上學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.73,0:14:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想去工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.50,0:14:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 媽媽說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.87,0:14:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只有中學畢業而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.08,0:14:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我也想當個女高中生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.85,0:15:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.05,0:15:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要代替我擁有快樂的高中生活哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.12,0:15:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道從什麼時候開始 我知道媽媽是為了我而工作的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.13,0:15:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我卻沒有對媽媽說路上小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.34,0:15:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連她要去工作的背影都沒能看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.45,0:15:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以 至少要把高中…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.62,0:15:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把媽媽夢寐以求能夠就讀的高中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.36,0:15:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,順利地唸到畢業
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.80,0:15:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我的目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.44,0:16:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不會被發燒…打敗呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.99,0:16:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.86,0:16:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在學校裡總是充滿活力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.83,0:16:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我永遠看不到她辛苦的一面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.13,0:16:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我想脫離草摩家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.01,0:16:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果還不是一樣留在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.25,0:16:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的厭惡的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.78,0:16:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就該像本田同學一樣住在帳篷裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.62,0:16:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到祕境或是深山裡才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.06,0:16:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真是太天真了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.86,0:16:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說她太棒了 對小透很不禮貌喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.97,0:17:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.54,0:17:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來拜託你囉 我要出去一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.78,0:17:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去哪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.28,0:17:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫非你想把那個挖回來？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.48,0:17:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也去吧 一個人會很辛苦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.69,0:17:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.89,0:17:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰告訴你是一個人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.10,0:17:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.57,0:17:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.64,0:17:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳又發燒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.38,0:17:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要勉強幫忙做家事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.05,0:17:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳應該做妳自己 放輕鬆一點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.09,0:17:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天妳會美夢成真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.46,0:18:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.83,0:18:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要表現得像自己一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.91,0:18:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.08,0:18:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.28,0:18:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.95,0:18:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還好吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.66,0:18:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 早！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.96,0:18:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳的行李應該全部挖出來了 要不要確認一下？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.53,0:18:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？草摩同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.40,0:18:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一個人去沙土堆裡!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.00,0:18:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.17,0:18:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 你是怎麼辦到的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.14,0:18:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祕密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.34,0:18:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.68,0:18:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好髒的房子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.54,0:18:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.81,0:18:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然住的全是男孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.78,0:18:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過二樓剛好有間空房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.18,0:19:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在房子改建好之前 妳可以先住在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.99,0:19:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.82,0:19:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不、不行…我反對！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.99,0:19:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,房間可以上鎖啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.29,0:19:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我、我不是說這個啦 該怎麼說才好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.33,0:19:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳喜歡做家事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.90,0:19:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像是掃地、煮飯什麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.73,0:19:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個…是啊 我很喜歡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.47,0:19:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到草摩家——！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.64,0:19:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也去幫妳搬行李囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.84,0:19:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由希 你的衣服借她換嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.24,0:19:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不、不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.21,0:19:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經麻煩你們照顧我了 現在又要把房間借我住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.41,0:19:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實在太打擾你們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.08,0:19:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本田同學 是我們自己開口的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.32,0:19:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳就別再想什麼打擾不打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.16,0:19:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更何況妳應該沒有地方去吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.29,0:19:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.56,0:19:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 請你們多教我一些事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.27,0:19:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比方說草摩家的規矩、慣例之類的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.77,0:19:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種事別放在心上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.70,0:19:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳應該做妳自己 在這裡放輕鬆一點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.51,0:20:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳應該做妳自己 放輕鬆一點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.79,0:20:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣真的好嗎？和女孩子一起住耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.49,0:20:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到現在還說這些做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.29,0:20:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安啦 只要別被抱住就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.97,0:20:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到轉眼間會有這麼大的變化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.60,0:20:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,彷彿在做夢似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.04,0:20:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連衣服都借給我穿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.74,0:20:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關太久了 有點霉味 打開窗戶透透氣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.49,0:20:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.63,0:20:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做好被我痛宰的準備了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.86,0:20:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死老鼠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.43,0:20:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還不死心啊？你太弱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.87,0:20:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,臭小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.03,0:20:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要是以為我還是吳下阿蒙的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.87,0:20:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就遭殃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.10,0:20:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我今天一定要痛扁你一頓！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.37,0:21:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.52,0:21:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由希 剛剛怎麼那麼吵 是不是夾來了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.02,0:21:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 你沒事吧？喂！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.32,0:21:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他變成貓了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.16,0:21:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是因為我撞他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.00,0:21:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撞錯地方才會變成貓!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.40,0:21:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 嗯 這個嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.63,0:21:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎樣 先送他到醫院吧！讓醫生為他治療！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.17,0:21:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本田同學！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.87,0:21:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.64,0:21:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.77,0:21:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.32,0:21:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.99,0:21:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都變成動物了
